data.description: *Assumable VA loan @2.25% for a VA buyer*Stunning 1-story prior Highland Model*Luxurious 1 owner home boasts 4 bdrms, 3.5 baths w/media room+dedicated office and designer finishes. Abundance of natural light w/8 ft windows and 13 ft ceilings. Elegance and charm flows in this open concept home. Beautifully appointed kitchen w/enormous island, generous work space and storage, perfect for entertaining and casual dining. Enjoy movie night in the  theater room where the surround sound equipment, DVD player, TV and speaker system remain. Home hardwired w/security and sound system. 3 car tandem garage, insulated and climate controlled with enhanced lighting. Extended covered patio for outdoor comfort!
